I was disappointed in this recipe. I didn't mind the preparation, but this cake just wasn't worth it. Baking for 35 minutes is was too long! I took mine out in 30 minutes and it was still dry. The frosting was fine, I did whip it over ice longer than the recipe called for and then beat it with the electric mixer. I would make this same frosting for a better chocolate cake recipe. But, I don't think I'll try this cake again.

